methods.getClientDoSubscribeDescriptor:
Fetch the client side descriptor for a specific table schema.

Note: Java generics information - <Options>

:param options: (Options) - the set of options that last across the entire life of the subscription
:param columnChunkTypes: (io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.ChunkType[]) - the chunk types per column
:param columnTypes: (java.lang.Class<?>[]) - the class type per column
:param componentTypes: (java.lang.Class<?>[]) - the component class type per column
:param streamReader: (io.deephaven.grpc_api.barrage.BarrageMessageConsumer.StreamReader<Options>) - the stream reader - intended to be thread safe and re-usable
:return: (io.grpc.MethodDescriptor<io.deephaven.proto.backplane.grpc.SubscriptionRequest,io.deephaven.db.v2.utils.BarrageMessage>) the client side method descriptor
